Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad, want some caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l thought that was a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there. Are your parents around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! We're the Kusakabes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving in down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, there's a bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do you like the new place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this. A tunnel of trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it could be haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's a huge tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a camphor tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Camphor tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Camphor tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,An acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't open the screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Acorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are acorns in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They dropped from up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are squirrels in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Squirrels, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rats that like acorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have squirrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll open the door for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Satsuki, open up the kitchen.\N-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just around the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathtubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's something in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A squirrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not bugs or mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They were black and they were all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were... dust bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dust bunnies"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in my picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts don't come out on days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When you walk into a dark room from outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,your eyes dim and so the dust bunnies come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, dust bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out, wherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See if you can find a way to get upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up there and open all the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dust bunnies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Another acorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, dust bunnies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Dustbunny-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's definitely something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to live in a\Nhaunted house ever since I was a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it. Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our new neighbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She takes care of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She takes care of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Satsuki and this is my sister, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry l didn't have time\Nto clean up a bit more before you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've done plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been very busy in the rice fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but l did manage to keep\Nthe place well dusted, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, what have you done to your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The dust bunny got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine are black, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the "soot sprites".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Soot sprites?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The black puff balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They scurry everywhere when you enter a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in old, empty houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and run all over the place,\Ncovering everything with dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,l used to be able to see them when l was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've seen them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they like ghosts or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, dear. They're nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If they decide that you're nice people,\Nthey won't harm you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and after a while, they'll just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now they're probably deciding where to go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, they're going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if a huge one comes out, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. I won't walk you to the bathroom at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, cleaning time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get some water from the stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, it's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, keep pumping 'til the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... my Mum... for Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You live in a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the same when I was his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really love Granny's rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, the house is going to fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not. We've only just moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, try laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then whatever scares you will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it. I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:21:00.64,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two, one-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, keep up the good work...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Washing... finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you all heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To visit Mummy in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her my regards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So glad you came, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy took the wrong road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Hello, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a school holiday, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy is talking to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to see you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you settled into the new house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, do you like ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei was worried that you wouldn't like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you fixing Mei's hair, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky girl, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But she always gets mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you won't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't yours too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I like it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do mine, Mummy! Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wavy hair, just like mine when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be like yours when I grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably. You take after your Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum looked really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor says she'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.68,0:24:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon? Like tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is a little too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum said she'll sleep with me in my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.28,0:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you saying you're big enough to sleep alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum is special!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, time to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.53,0:25:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I overslept again...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.26,0:25:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to bring a box lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.57,0:25:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.08,0:25:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made something for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.70,0:25:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.67,0:25:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.45,0:25:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.00,0:25:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, sit down and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.25,0:25:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.38,0:25:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.51,0:25:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Satsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.49,0:25:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.06,0:26:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a friend already?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.00,0:26:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's Michiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.36,0:26:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.37,0:26:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.33,0:26:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.43,0:26:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.55,0:26:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.31,0:26:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look all grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.75,0:26:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.72,0:26:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And where might you be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.29,0:27:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, is it lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.48,0:27:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be the flower shop, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.46,0:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadpoles!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.43,0:28:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Got no bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.45,0:33:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A big dust bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To-to-ro? You're Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.78,0:34:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're Totoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.98,0:35:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.82,0:35:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.40,0:35:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.25,0:35:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. Is it that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.17,0:35:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.86,0:35:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to Michiko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:35:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't eaten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.89,0:36:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mei in the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.51,0:36:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.92,0:36:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.86,0:36:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.21,0:36:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.81,0:36:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I found her hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.87,0:36:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.66,0:36:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.83,0:36:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.84,0:36:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.97,0:36:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.62,0:36:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.44,0:37:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.23,0:37:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that troll in your picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.42,0:37:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.46,0:37:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was all hairy with a big mouth like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.61,0:37:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a tiny one and a little one and a huge one like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.12,0:37:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.80,0:37:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.38,0:37:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A great hiding place!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.84,0:37:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Mei said she met a Totoro here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Totoro?\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.09,0:37:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.64,0:37:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.30,0:37:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.90,0:37:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.90,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.70,0:37:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It went to a big tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't any other path.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.87,0:38:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.86,0:38:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.95,0:38:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.22,0:38:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true! Totoro was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.72,0:38:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.28,0:38:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.03,0:38:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.82,0:38:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Neither of us think you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.49,0:38:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably met the king of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.11,0:38:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You were very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.71,0:38:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't come out very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.19,0:38:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We should pay our respects at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.62,0:38:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay our respects?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.61,0:38:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.19,0:39:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, you're getting heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.91,0:39:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, look! That camphor tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.78,0:39:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.27,0:39:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.54,0:39:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.19,0:39:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.59,0:39:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.93,0:39:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The hole has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.20,0:39:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.06,0:39:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The hole disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.13,0:39:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you he doesn't come to see us often.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.53,0:40:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But will he come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.24,0:40:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree must have stood here for years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees and people used to be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.38,0:40:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that tree and fell in love with the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that Mum likes it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.47,0:40:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's pay our respects and then get home for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.85,0:40:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I promised to go see Michiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.43,0:40:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.10,0:40:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.65,0:40:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for looking after Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.42,0:40:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.45,0:40:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's race home!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.01,0:40:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.49,0:40:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.54,0:40:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.57,0:40:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.79,0:41:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Mother, something amazing happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.17,0:41:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mei met a giant Totoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.51,0:41:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm hoping to see him myself soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.17,0:41:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta, hurry up! You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.52,0:41:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.90,0:42:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.89,0:42:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.07,0:42:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.14,0:42:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.92,0:42:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.53,0:42:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She insisted to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.91,0:42:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dad's day at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.53,0:42:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to be a good girl at Granny's.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.42,0:43:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have two more classes\Nand Granny's too busy for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.13,0:43:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She was good up 'til now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.48,0:43:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and talk to my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.86,0:43:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Satsuki-san's mother is in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.53,0:43:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you all to be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.04,0:43:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.70,0:43:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Totoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.60,0:43:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, you should keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.64,0:43:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.02,0:44:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.94,0:44:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay after class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.59,0:44:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We'll let the teacher know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.63,0:44:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.88,0:44:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.82,0:44:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, it's going to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.54,0:44:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.34,0:44:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.22,0:44:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.49,0:44:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I good?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.51,0:44:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.10,0:44:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.86,0:44:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Guardian Spirit, let us stay until the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.91,0:45:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.59,0:45:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.32,0:45:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.64,0:46:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got holes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.90,0:46:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.49,0:46:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I better give Daddy's his umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.11,0:46:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.03,0:46:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I forgot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.07,0:46:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What idiot forgets his umbrella on a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.87,0:46:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke it, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.89,0:46:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.43,0:46:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.06,0:46:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Satsuki-san. Hi, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.41,0:46:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.23,0:46:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about Mei today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.88,0:46:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Sorry we couldn't do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.20,0:47:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta lent us this umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.49,0:47:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He lent you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.60,0:47:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A broken old thing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.54,0:47:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei was with me, so I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.86,0:47:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so sorry that Kanta got wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.81,0:47:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.98,0:47:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably cleaned him up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.03,0:47:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you off to meet your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.54,0:47:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.27,0:47:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What good girls you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.18,0:47:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.79,0:47:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.15,0:47:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.00,0:47:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.97,0:47:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.55,0:47:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.17,0:48:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.23,0:48:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy wasn't on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.62,0:48:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be on the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.76,0:48:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wait at Granny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.89,0:48:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.15,0:49:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.97,0:49:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.93,0:49:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to wait at Granny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.98,0:49:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.11,0:49:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.15,0:49:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That bus sure is late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.41,0:49:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.16,0:51:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.38,0:51:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.77,0:51:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.44,0:51:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it. Mei's slipping off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.94,0:51:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.68,0:53:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.34,0:54:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro took Daddy's umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.11,0:54:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.81,0:54:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.49,0:54:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My train was delayed,\Nso l had to wait for the next bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.41,0:54:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.62,0:54:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We met him, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.04,0:54:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.99,0:54:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cat bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.17,0:54:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.57,0:54:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.38,0:54:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With big eyes like these!\N-Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.26,0:54:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We met him!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.67,0:54:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We met Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.98,0:55:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.06,0:55:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.53,0:55:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Mother, I can't tell you how excited I was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.44,0:55:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the scariest, funniest day I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.51,0:55:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Totoro gave us a lovely present...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.96,0:55:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...wrapped in bamboo leaves\Nand tied with dragon whiskers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.43,0:55:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we opened it,\Nit was full of magic nuts and seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.06,0:55:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"We decided to plant them in the\Ngarden to make a lovely forest. But..."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.23,0:55:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...they haven't sprouted yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.27,0:56:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mei sits there all day, waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.99,0:56:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looks like a little crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.75,0:56:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nearly summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.74,0:56:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mother, get well soon. Love, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.47,0:56:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Bed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights off!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.41,0:56:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.33,0:56:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do you think they will sprout tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.54,0:56:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Totoro would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.32,0:56:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.45,0:57:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.68,0:57:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where we planted the seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.00,0:59:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.76,1:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, we're the wind!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.61,1:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no trees!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.88,1:01:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.84,1:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.00,1:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.41,1:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.44,1:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.59,1:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.41,1:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusakabe-san! Telegram!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.66,1:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusakabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.03,1:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Telegram!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.37,1:02:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.88,1:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.26,1:02:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.68,1:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.95,1:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.63,1:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.20,1:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your garden's a treasure house.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.17,1:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.51,1:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These should be cold now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.72,1:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.81,1:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.28,1:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The sun blessed these\Nso they're really good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.41,1:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Would they help my Mum, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.41,1:03:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.85,1:03:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If she eats my vegetables, she'll get better right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.85,1:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's supposed to be back on saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.58,1:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll sleep in my bed!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.37,1:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. At last. That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.35,1:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only for a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.20,1:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To get used to the new house.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.20,1:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She will go back on monday.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.14,1:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.63,1:04:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give her lots of vegetables, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.27,1:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her this corn I picked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.05,1:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.33,1:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.36,1:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a telegram for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.61,1:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.75,1:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad won't be back till late. What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.59,1:04:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it, it might be important.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.10,1:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please contact, hospital...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.16,1:04:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Mom's hospital!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.37,1:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happened to her!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.48,1:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.33,1:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.69,1:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.63,1:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where your Dad is?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.90,1:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know his office number,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.92,1:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't have a telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.30,1:05:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta, take her to use the phone in the main house!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.71,1:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.62,1:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei, stay here with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.71,1:05:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with Granny, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.21,1:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'd like to make a long-distance call, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.82,1:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tokyo 31 -1 382.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.74,1:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.97,1:06:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A cute girl, Kanta.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.48,1:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.95,1:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.06,1:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, may I speak to Dad... er... Mr. Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.86,1:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his daughter, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.70,1:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.88,1:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.77,1:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.14,1:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.83,1:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.71,1:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll call them right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.88,1:06:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with Mum? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.83,1:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.06,1:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check and call you right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.10,1:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.32,1:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.72,1:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging up now. Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.69,1:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,May I stay here until he calls back?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.77,1:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.45,1:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.25,1:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this corn is for my Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.88,1:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my Mom's!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.32,1:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.28,1:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's not well so she's not coming home this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.00,1:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.33,1:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.75,1:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want her to get worse, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.40,1:08:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.17,1:08:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.50,1:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.34,1:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't care if she dies, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.84,1:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.09,1:08:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being silly!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.40,1:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.48,1:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.15,1:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.43,1:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should bring the washing in...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.76,1:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.58,1:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny's here to help, so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.05,1:09:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Dad said that he'll stop\Nby the hospital to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.36,1:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's just a cold. She'll be back next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.46,1:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it was just a cold...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.18,1:09:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when she went into the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.39,1:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if she dies!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.31,1:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.89,1:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mum will...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.73,1:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Nobody would leave two pretty little girls like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.57,1:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.33,1:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here until Daddy comes back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.08,1:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.51,1:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.60,1:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.47,1:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.83,1:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she at the bus stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.56,1:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.28,1:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has she gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.16,1:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I yelled at her, because she was being silly...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.09,1:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's heading for the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.66,1:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.20,1:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take a grown-up 3 hours!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.97,1:11:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.33,1:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.17,1:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your dad that Mei-chan is missing!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.18,1:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Mei.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.33,1:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Always getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.94,1:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.08,1:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.04,1:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a little girl pass by?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.04,1:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.78,1:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.56,1:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I would've noticed...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.01,1:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.15,1:12:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she came this way?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.43,1:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.40,1:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.81,1:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.19,1:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.71,1:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.05,1:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a little girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.51,1:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.78,1:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's heading to the hospital. She's only 4.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.95,1:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.48,1:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We just came from there...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.23,1:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we didn't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.96,1:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.76,1:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.65,1:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,From Matsugo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.89,1:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsugo?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.64,1:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It's very far away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.72,1:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.28,1:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.45,1:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanta!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.71,1:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.47,1:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.95,1:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and the others are looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.29,1:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the hospital. You should go back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.34,1:14:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she got lost on the way to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.67,1:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They found a sandal by the pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.72,1:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not sure if it's hers or not!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.70,1:14:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.78,1:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, please protect her and...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.37,1:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too deep here, better search further away!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.16,1:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are there any poles left?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.88,1:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, Satsuki's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.72,1:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.56,1:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, is it hers?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.73,1:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.54,1:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. I was sure it was hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.22,1:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Granny was jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.11,1:16:27.42,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's not hers!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.95,1:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's she gone then?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.75,1:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.42,1:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We better hurry. It'll be dark soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.17,1:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate your help, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.93,1:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Could have been any of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.92,1:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help me Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.21,1:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei is lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dark soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.59,1:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's scared somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.83,1:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.88,1:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Totoro, Mei is lost and we can't find her!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.38,1:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be scared. Please help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.18,1:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.28,1:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people can't see the bus!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.55,1:19:53.10,Notes,,0,0,0,,FOREST-SWAMP
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.10,1:19:54.60,Notes,,0,0,0,,CEMETERY-SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.73,1:20:00.05,Notes,,0,0,0,,Mei
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.65,1:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.58,1:20:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The trees are moving out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.80,1:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.24,1:21:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.38,1:21:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.99,1:21:13.48,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.22,1:21:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.43,1:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.26,1:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.23,1:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.48,1:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to take the corn to Mum?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.51,1:21:48.20,Notes,,0,0,0,,Hospital
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.95,1:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take us to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.25,1:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.89,1:22:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.24,1:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't need to send a telegram just for a cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.97,1:22:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.78,1:22:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to upset them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.62,1:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine. As long as you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.48,1:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all learned to cope.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.62,1:22:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll just postpone the enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.07,1:22:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They've put up with it so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.77,1:22:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm especially sorry for Satsuki. She's been so patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.79,1:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.70,1:22:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to spoil them for a while when I come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.85,1:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.26,1:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.25,1:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.71,1:22:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.97,1:23:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.86,1:23:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.32,1:23:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.74,1:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.45,1:23:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,l thought l saw Satsuki and Mei\Nsmiling at us from up in that tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.92,1:23:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds crazy, but maybe you did. Look at this.
